facility_name: The name of the facility for which the energy costs are being tracked.
total_energy_cost: The total energy cost incurred by the facility for the specified period, given in Canadian dollars.
average_cost_per_kWh: The average cost per kilowatt-hour (kWh) of energy consumed by the facility.
energy_consumption_kWh: The total energy consumption of the facility in kilowatt-hours (kWh) during the specified period.
reporting_period: The time period for which the energy costs and consumption are reported, e.g., 'Q2 2024'.
